Description: Interface to Gen3 data discovery and query services with
    the NHGRI AnVIL computational cloud. Functionality includes
    user-friendly authentication and basic data discovery (study,
    particpant, sample information) as well as support for direct
    GraphQL queries. Also included is developer-oriented access to the
    main Gen3 RESTful interfaces.
